summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the condemnation proceedings to acquire property and property rights for electric transmission line purposes as provided in Ordinance 97963, King County Cause No. 715585, and in King County Cause No. 705924, Robert L. Edwards et ux. v. City, accepting the stipulation and condemnation award settling the matters in controversy in said proceedings, and making an appropriation from the Light Fund therefor.
